.section.instructions 
  .title Compose
  div.help 
    .label Help Â»
  .moreHelp
    p Notes consist of the numbers 1 through 8 corresponding to the sounds of the instrument above. These notes use the middle octave.
    p To specify the high octave, surround the notes with parenthesis: (1 23 55)
    p To specify the low octave, surround the notes with brackets: [851 99]
    p The delay between each note played is determined by the tempo. Spaces indicate pauses with the duration of a single note.
    p You can chain spaces together to lengthen the time between notes being played: 176&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;28 (12) [518](111)
  div
    textarea.notation(placeholder = "Type notes here")
    div
      .tempoLabel Tempo (in milliseconds)
      input.tempo(type = "text", value = "300")
    .play Play
  div
    .permalinkLabel Permalink
    span
      input.autoplay(type = "checkbox", id = "autoplay", name = "autoplay")
      label.autoplayLabel(for = "autoplay") Autoplay on page load
      input.permalink(type = "text")
    
